@(A.22 = 22-27) I gazed over all the people, and chose @wDN{Dumuzid} as god of the Land. For @wDN{Dumuzid}, beloved by @wDN{Enlil}, I exalted his name and decreed his destiny. My mother cherishes him constantly, and my father speaks his praise.

